text.section:
The Department shall increase the rate of reimbursement for community services providers by an amount that:
Reduces the disparity amount to 80% on or before July 1, 2002;
Reduces the disparity amount to 62% on or before July 1, 2003;
Reduces the disparity amount to 40% on or before July 1, 2004;
Reduces the disparity amount to 20% on or before July 1, 2005; and
Eliminates the disparity amount on or before July 1, 2006.
